      "releaseNotes": "Thanks for using the AMC Theatres App! To make sure you don't miss the latest improvements, keep your Automatic Updates turned on.\n\nIn this version:\n- a few small bug fixes and stability improvements\n\nHave feedback or suggestions? Send us a message in the app (Menu -> Feedback & Support -> App Feedback)\n\nSee you at the movies!",
